name: Talisker Resources Ltd. Common share purchase warrants
longDescription: Talisker Resources Ltd is a junior resource company in British Columbia. Its projects include the Bralorne Gold Complex, an advanced stage project with exploration potential from a historical high-grade gold producing mine as well as its Spences Bridge Project, among other projects. The company operates in the business segment of mineral exploration and evaluation in British Columbia, Canada.
